        "evidence": "<p>Admit if&nbsp;<span>any</span> of the following are present:</p> <div class=\"table-responsive\"> <table class=\"table table-bordered\"> <tbody> <tr> <td> <p><span>BNP Level </span><span>≥300 pg/ml</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p><span>Bradycardia </span></p> <p><span>*≤50 bpm in ED or pre-hospital</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p><span>Rectal examination showing fecal occult blood</span></p> <p><span>*If suspicion of gastrointestinal bleed</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p><span>Anemia</span></p> <p><span>*Hemoglobin ≤90 g/l</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p><span>Chest pain</span></p> <p><span>*Associated with syncope</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p><span>ECG showing Q wave</span></p> <p><span>*Not in lead III</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <p><span>Saturation ≤94% on room air</span></p> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </div>",
